ldn't have asked for stuff, but they're very generous and I'd not have been able to refuse.  I'm not playing nearly as much as I did then, too.  I used to be as fanatical about leveling and the end-game as FnF folks are here.  EQ is more of a hobby this time. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uwearelegion.showPublicProfile?language=EN>We Are Legion</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://home.earthlink.net/~lazurith/Cris.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 14<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/28/02 7:35:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1214.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.earthlink.net/~lazurith/Crissnakk.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Friends would be a big reason, I'd guess</span><hr size=1> Wow, very good points one and all!<br>
